to another level.

1291
01:29:51,810 --> 01:29:53,035
But...

1292
01:29:53,869 --> 01:29:56,475
after I ran away from you,

1293
01:29:58,150 --> 01:29:59,845
I felt lonely.

1294
01:30:01,480 --> 01:30:05,044
You know you're my only friend.

1295
01:30:08,319 --> 01:30:12,785
After I ran away from
my only friend, schoolmate,

1296
01:30:14,130 --> 01:30:15,825
and the only guy...

