01:30:34,420 --> 01:30:36,814
- Yes.
- You're stupid.

1303
01:30:37,049 --> 01:30:39,385
It's impossible
to fill my space.

1304
01:30:39,889 --> 01:30:41,414
Whatever.

1305
01:30:48,159 --> 01:30:49,695
Du Ah.

1306
01:30:51,529 --> 01:30:53,294
Then how about now?

1307
01:30:53,469 --> 01:30:54,595
What?

1308
01:30:55,940 --> 01:30:58,405
I'm right here next to you.

1309
01:31:00,339 --> 01:31:03,575
