1312
01:31:16,420 --> 01:31:17,725
Han Wool.

1313
01:31:18,790 --> 01:31:19,925
Yes?

1314
01:31:20,730 --> 01:31:23,024
I think there's an expiry date...

1315
01:31:24,230 --> 01:31:26,865
