1318
01:31:36,940 --> 01:31:40,745
But I think that's because
we're friends.

1319
01:31:41,119 --> 01:31:43,914
We're so perfect as friends.

1320
01:31:44,350 --> 01:31:45,745
And I don't...

1321
01:31:47,690 --> 01:31:50,785
want to ruin what we have.

1322
01:31:52,889 --> 01:31:55,425
You think we're perfect as friends?

1323
01:31:58,429 --> 01:32:00,325
